[Freeze Timer]
author=bungholio
description=SELECT + L2 = On; SELECT + L1 = Off
Turn this off before starting an event. Turn it on while driving. The timer still counts down, but things won&#039;t be over until you turn the code off.
patch=1,EE,D049165C,extended,00400101
