[Infinite Boost]
author=bungholio
description=You can&#039;t chain burnouts with this.
patch=1,EE,21E89EA4,extended,44420000

[Infinite Supercharge]
author=bungholio
description=Perfect, and even better than infinite boost. The instant you do anything that would increase how much boost you have, you will get a full Supercharge. Those yellow blinking arrows that allow you to chain burnouts also instantly fill if you do anything that would increase your boost. All you need to do is drive into the oncoming traffic lane for an instant and you&#039;ll instantly have a full supercharge. You can chain burnouts with this.
patch=1,EE,21E89EB4,extended,7FFFFFFF

