[Turtoise Racers (Slow AI)]
author=bungholio
description=Default value 38630001, just in case you want to toggle it on/off.
You might not want this on for Road Rage events, it is hard take out an opponent because they are moving too slow. They move so slow, it is impossible for you to lose a race.
